headline: J.B. Hunt Among Newsweek’s America’s Most Reliable Companies 2025
summary: LOWELL, Ark., December 04, 2024--J.B. Hunt Transport Services Inc. (NASDAQ: JBHT), one of the largest supply chain solutions providers in North America, has been named to Newsweek’s list of America’s Most Reliable Companies 2025, recognizing the company’s integrity, commitment to service quality and say-do culture. This prestigious award is presented in collaboration with Statista, the world-leading statistics portal and industry ranking provider.
